8-11-02T10:24:01.000Z","msg":"你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=%2FwvC0QD7q%2Bc%2B2coBXKGRyS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=1356c17d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！"},{"pid":"6a9466de8b5a8cc0cda7fa5d64527f5ec7f29faa","tid":886731,"uid":55019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T10:26:11.000Z","msg":"不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a606e1e7a0dbc51c394af134bb27541d660ba06a","tid":886731,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T10:27:07.000Z","msg":"tldr"},{"pid":"9a9d4e19c7a920af5f033a3a9789c059a0646d91","tid":886731,"uid":29148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T10:27:43.000Z","msg":"相信你心中一定非常痛苦，才會如此寫下你的心聲！雖然，我並未完全了解你，但我明白置身痛苦中是怎樣一回事。有些人在困苦之中，會選擇放棄自己，不知道你是否也有這自殺的念頭？<br />\n<br />\n無論你是否想過放棄自己，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡。因為人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。你不如停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=%2FwvC0QD7q%2Bc%2B2coBXKGRyS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=1356c17d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"470d4747662024d4d7f576773572fc359aa1fe45","tid":886731,"uid":167832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T10:28:51.000Z","msg":"襯後生轉基"},{"pid":"82399cd4450522401937da58874c496194d14e69","tid":886731,"uid":55019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"470d4747662024d4d7f576773572fc359aa1fe45","tid":886731,"uid":167832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T10:28:51.000Z","msg":"襯後生轉基"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T10:33:36.000Z","msg":"Ching sick ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe63f6744eb5d4f50a5b404e17ec3f1b1803563","tid":886731,"uid":167832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82399cd4450522401937da58874c496194d14e69","tid":886731,"uid":55019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"470d4747662024d4d7f576773572fc359aa1fe45","tid":886731,"uid":167832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T10:28:51.000Z","msg":"襯後生轉基"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T10:33:36.000Z","msg":"Ching sick ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T13:10:35.000Z","msg":"基不可失"},{"pid":"6905b537c5c8582d0e16f66d3c4fe172ed1dfc59","tid":886731,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T13:14:19.000Z","msg":"估錯  以為係 切左碌鳩"}]}